/>"},{"pid":"8e7380bffa5c5a225e05ab2a5a96f8ab970e7bbd","tid":269923,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:02:40.000Z","msg":"肯亞網友留言<br />\n已經屌緊中國援建果條蒙內鐵路(SGR)<br />\n<br />\nSam Luvai &middot; Import Customs Clearing Agent at Maragoli Welfare Association - Mombasa Island<br />\nWe went for cheap n fake designed to confuse poor kenyans<br />\nLike &middot; Reply &middot; Jun 1, 2017 8:49pm<br />\n<br />\nFranklin Ogise &middot; KISII UNIVERSITY<br />\nGermany machines are the best...too bad we don't seem to make better choices<br />\nLike &middot; Reply &middot; Jun 1, 2017 8:58pm<br />\n<br />\nEmily Were &middot; Works at Self<br />\nThe same china wenye SGR hatari<br />\nLike &middot; Reply &middot; Jun 1, 2017 9:22pm<br />\n<br />\nPaul Moiruri &middot; University of Nairobi<br />\nChina is here to exploit Kenya .n it doing it by colonizing our minds .<br />\nLike &middot; Reply &middot; 1 &middot; Jun 1, 2017 9:26pm<br />\n<br />\nMarc Korir<br />\nVitu fake za china, uhuru kukimbilia mali raisi raisi abaki na change<br />\nLike &middot; Reply &middot; 4 &middot; Jun 1, 2017 9:31pm<br />\n<br />\nAlex Mwango &middot; Animator at Tropical village and resort<br />\nEagerly waiting for the sgr<br />\nLike &middot; Reply &middot; 1 &middot; Jun 1, 2017 10:38pm<br />\n<br />\nEdwin Junior Mutua &middot; Palencia, Guatemala, Guatemala<br />\nSGR now its vehicles<br />\nLike &middot; Reply &middot; Jun 2, 2017 12:01am<br />\n<br />\nDouglas Otieno Onoka<br />\nLove for short cut, and cheap things. I don't trust the SGR, I know one day we will realize that we have been duped and it will be too late.<br />\nLike &middot; Reply &middot; Jun 2, 2017 4:13am<br />\n<br />\nJakisumo Hezzy &middot; Maseno University<br />\nFake machines that makes our boys die<br />\nLike &middot; Reply &middot; Jun 2, 2017 5:00am<br />\n<br />\nDavid Too &middot; University of constans confusion.(ucc)<br />\nI think it's time we buy them from Russia. The Russians supply the real thing<br />\nLike &middot; Reply &middot; Jun 2, 2017 10:38am<br />\n<br />\nErick Isiaho &middot; Works at Self-Employed<br />\nChinas are special for making spoons<br />\nLike &middot; Reply &middot; Jun 2, 2017 2:11pm<br />\n<br />\nJackie Muchemo &middot; Bondo Teachers Training College<br />\nHahaha! China will kill us. Hatakano...<br />\nLike &middot; Reply &middot; Jun 3, 2017 6:23am"},{"pid":"bc1465b7cc00740086124ff280c9368b514507a4","tid":269923,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:04:05.000Z","msg":"專搵水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9413fb16d10019fc49a064d51558030be2165d1","tid":269923,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:05:44.000Z","msg":"笑死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04eae760bb10ee358aefc193284248858d6809ea","tid":269923,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:15:45.000Z","msg":"有歐美貨唔用<br />\n用大陸貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n貪平你咪死人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地堆技術係2戰發展出黎<br />\n大陸2戰個陣做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb401e1621c95c087ea848c6fa22e366e159a090","tid":269923,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:19:35.000Z","msg":"支那啱啱先打飛機話做好肯亞鐵路<br />\n<br />\n遲D有野睇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e83b376d45bb56349a7cf5f49d2e8d88ed971a","tid":269923,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T04:35:14.000Z","msg":"未派上打真軍死全隊咪算好囉"},{"pid":"757a064519bedd9682ba4c9faabc0f010687f8e1","tid":269923,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor